        <p>
            <note>DDNS allows you to access your network using domain names instead of IP address.
                The service manages changing IP address and updates your domain information
                dynamically. You must sign up for service through <xref
                    href="http://www.dyndns.com/" format="html" scope="external">dyndns.org</xref>,
                    <xref href="http://freedns.afraid.org/" format="html" scope="external"
                    >freedns.afraid.org</xref>, <xref href="http://www.no-ip.com/" format="html"
                    scope="external">www.no-ip.com</xref>, <xref href="http://www.zoneedit.com/"
                    format="html" scope="external">www.zoneedit.com</xref>.</note>
        </p>
